videos.description: Arizona State's Remy Martin flops hard to draw the offensive foul call on Rob Edwards of Georgia.
videos.headline: ASU's Martin flops to sell foul call

videos.description: Georgia's Nicolas Claxton gets the ball on the cut to the basket and dunks it home to cut the ASU lead to 73-72 late in the second half.
videos.headline: Claxton has big-time dunk
